<p>The queen (Mary) made an  <QUOTE> entry towards the tower</QUOTE>  the above year: upon which occasion the front of the church was hung with arras towards Fenchurch-street. The expense of putting it up was <measure value="4d." type=currency><num value="4">4</num>d.</measure> and the cost <measure value="20s." type=currency><num value="20">20</num>s.</measure> 
