<ITEM>Item, all thewyndowes glaysed. <ITEM>Item, <num value="1">one</num> banner. <ITEM>Item, <num value="3">three</num> scutcheons. <ITEM>Item, a lattes, with the appurtenances. 
</LIST>
 
